Title: Some Remarks on the Quantization of Gauge Theories

Comments: 8 pages. RevTex (two-column), no figures. The dvi version can be

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 37 (1996) 1713-1723; Erratum-ibid. 37 (1996) 6590

The methods of reduced phase space quantization and Dirac quantization areexamined in a simple gauge theory. A condition for the possible equivalence ofthe two methods is discussed.